The Northern Youth Advocacy for Excellence (NYAE) has endorsed Hon. Ahmed Wase for the position of Deputy Speaker of the House of Representatives in the 9th National Assembly. The group, which made the endorsement at its annual northern leadership award forum yesterday in Abuja, extolled Wase’s virtues as an astute administrator which it argued qualified him for the task. The National President of NYAE, Comrade Husseni Usman, at the forum, described Hon. Wase as a man of value whose visionary leadership qualities produced inspiration beyond his home state of Plateau.  ‘Gbajabiamila, Wase perfect combination for speakership’ Speakership: Group drums support for Wase …Youth group insists on Wase Dear Esteemed reader, As part of our drive to keep improving the content of our newspaper, we are conducting a readership survey to enable us serve you better. Kindly take two minutes of your time to fill in this questionnaire. Thank you for your time. Click here to begin